      "beast_baseline": "small pockets of silence aren't enough anymore. it's like every time i find a moment of quiet, the debt of everything i haven't achieved just catches up to me. i'm not looking for a nap or a weekend away. i'm looking for an end to the noise. i'm looking for a way to finally, truly, be done with the struggle. is there even a version of this where i don't have to keep performing or fighting?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
